{"id": "1388440500310245386", "channel_id": "1388440500310245386", "type": 0, "author_id": "534037660986114048", "author_name": "firepanda95", "author_bot": false, "content": "Pic 1 Onyx Plume -> Leigh Strike (23 dmg) - Damage Counter Increases by 23 (Corrosion Stack decreases by 23) instead of the health lost\nPic 2 Onyx Plume (Enemy Health is 808, Corrosion stacks is 1770, Damage Counter is 233)\nI'm not sure if this is a bug or not, but it can make some of the stage objectives with *deal x dmg in one turn* tricky to clear", "timestamp": "2025-06-28T08:46:51.251000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-06-28T08:47:16.571000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1388440500843053117", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-06-28_164028.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3239760, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1388440500310245386/1388440500843053117/Screenshot_2025-06-28_164028.png?ex=69cc32bb&is=69cae13b&hm=c5de2eabadaf92e110996e6dd512b5b0dde4972049e41c029b36123e85b9ad58&"}, {"id": "1388440501505757264", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-06-28_164001.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3090801, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1388440500310245386/1388440501505757264/Screenshot_2025-06-28_164001.png?ex=69cc32bb&is=69cae13b&hm=3b6821e6355305d42d55bbaa133917f664ffd57aefad60a9a35c52e614722564&"}, {"id": "1388440501983641661", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-06-28_163115.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 301914, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1388440500310245386/1388440501983641661/Screenshot_2025-06-28_163115.png?ex=69cc32bb&is=69cae13b&hm=0587cfcfd60f96beeac2638057b9afc6e8a216e9475498ea8f9dd8233bb3cd87&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1388440500310245386", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Corrosion damage not counted in Damage counter", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
